@startuml
title 自动生成：系统用例图
left to right direction

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 15
skinparam ranksep 40
skinparam usecase {
    BackgroundColor #F9F9F9
    BorderColor #333333
    ArrowColor #666666
}
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #333333
}


actor "学生"

